# Requirements (30 Points):

The Page must have the following Sections 

1. General  
   1. The page must have 4 “sections”, as shown \- 1 pts  
   2. These sections must use the same css styling \- 1pts  
   3. They must have a border \- 1pts  
2. Alert Me Section  
   1. There must be a form \- 1 pts  
   2. This form must take in a name, and it must be required to submit \- 1 pt  
   3. The form should have a button called “Alert Me” \- 1pts  
   4. When the “Alert Me” button is clicked it should take the Inputted name, and show an alert on the page saying “Hi Name\!” \- 4pts  
      1. Note this should be using a Javascript Function  
3. Change Color Section  
   1. There must be a button called Change Color \-1 pts  
   2. This button must change the color of the page and alternate \- 5pts  
      1. Ex: If page is blue it should be green, and if page is green it should be blue  
      2. Note this should be using a Javascript Function  
   3. Additionally the page should STAY the color that it swaps too \- 2 pts  
4. Text Tester Section  
   1. There must be a form \- 1 pts  
   2. The form should have a button called “Validate Text” \- 1pts  
   3. When the “Validate Text” button is clicked it should validate that the text has no special characters \- 6pts  
      1. Code: 

```javascript
var validation = /[!@#$%^&*()_+\-=\[\]{};':"\\|,.<>\/?]+/;
```

      2. It should alert if there is a Special Character  
      3. Note this should be using a Javascript Function  
5. Add Text Section  
   1. There must be a button called Add Text  \-1 pts  
   2. When this button is clicked, the heading of the page should be modified and the words “Add Text” should be added to it \- 4pts  
      1. Note this should be using a Javascript Function
